  "description": "Experience the ultimate Lake Travis bachelor party boat cruise in Austin with Premier Party Cruises. Our ATX Disco Cruise offers three exceptional packages designed specifically for bachelor parties: Basic Bach at $85 per person includes professional DJ, photographer, and all essentials; Disco King at $95 per person is our most popular package with premium perks and the groom cruises FREE with 16+ guests; Super Sparkle Platinum at $105 per person includes VIP treatment and the groom cruises FREE with 16+ guests. Every bachelor party cruise features a 4-hour Lake Travis experience with professional DJ spinning all day, professional photographer capturing epic moments, BYOB cooler setup with ice, giant lily pad floats, party supplies, and an electric party atmosphere with other bachelor groups. Perfect for groups of 20-40+ guests. Also available: private boat rentals for complete exclusivity ranging from 14-75 person capacity.",
